title: The Roald Dahl Audio Collection
description:
The Roald Dahl Audio Collection

Written and read by Roald Dahl 


Released by Penguin Audio in 2013

Length:  3 hours,  40 minutes


Roald Dahl's wickedly funny novels have turned him into the worlds number 1 storyteller. In this collection five splendiferous stories are brought to life by the author himself.



The Stories are:


Charlie and the Chocolate Factory  (Abridged)

James and the Giant Peach  (Abridged)

Fantastic Mr. Fox  (Unabridged)

The Enormous Crocodile  (Unabridged)

The Magic Finger  (Unabridged)
